					<text>After a moment, your crew tells you that these are simple beings, who enjoy a peaceful life. Your Slug puts the horse into a calm state, and you even manage to bring back a specimen. Without any fear of the horses, you explore further and even find old wreckage on the planet of an Engi ship, though the inhabitant is dead.</text>
